    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been a fantastic, reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully, making it perfect for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks great parked in the driveway. I\u2019ve kept up with the basics, and it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today. Come by and take a look\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
