    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup remains taut. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a valve lash adjustment to factory specifications. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain is optimized for peak performance and high-RPM reliability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
