    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2019 Audi A6 Premium Plus is a standout example of executive luxury and dependable performance. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Moonlight Blue Metallic that holds a deep, mirror-like gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway use, the body remains straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Nougat Brown leather and natural wood inlays. The upholstery is supple, the carpets are pristine, and the dual-screen MMI touch response system operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the turbocharged engine delivers smooth, responsive power, backed by a complete dealership service history. The vehicle sits on well-maintained alloy wheels with ample tire tread remaining. It has been smoke-free, garage-kept, and recently detailed, making it a reliable and sharp-looking choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
