      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a refined driving experience and proven mechanical reliability. The exterior retains its original luster, complemented by an interior that has been preserved with the utmost care. Rigorously inspected to meet our dealership\u2019s exacting standards, this automobile represents a premier choice for those seeking performance and poise. A distinguished addition to any collection.",
      "price": 36500.0,
